    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >街头巷尾备受热议的都市传说“轮椅彩芽”中的咒术仪式。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254990/extras/eb78471bc616189c068e9d3dde79807a.poster.avif?t=1765313826\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254990/extras/eb78471bc616189c068e9d3dde79807a.webm?t=1765313826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254990/extras/eb78471bc616189c068e9d3dde79807a.mp4?t=1765313826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公七海遥和主播高梨寝梦，通晓灵异问题的棺真里亚一起，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来到废弃医院，在直播时举行“轮椅彩芽”的咒术仪式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结果直播中断，遥等人突然消失。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正在观看直播的同学也前往废弃医院，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和遥等人一样，举行了“轮椅彩芽”的咒术仪式，结果所有人都晕了过去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们醒来时，身处与晕倒前似是而非的，被诅咒的废弃医院之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这可怕的废弃医院里，有仿徨的非人之物，充斥着肆虐的癫狂与怨念，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们能成功逃出去吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“轮椅彩芽”咒术仪式的真相究竟是……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254990/extras/c08f013e80f1a8495e5db46b5e00ca65.poster.avif?t=1765313826\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254990/extras/c08f013e80f1a8495e5db46b5e00ca65.webm?t=1765313826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254990/extras/c08f013e80f1a8495e5db46b5e00ca65.mp4?t=1765313826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恐怖派对再次来临。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传说中的恐怖游戏《尸体派对》时隔约九年，推出系列全新作品，故事发生在“废弃医院”之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的舞台，新的角色，又一次为您献上新的绝望故事。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >令人背脊发凉的恐怖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视觉小说富有冲击性的剧本，刺激且恐怖的描写，双耳人头立体声以及令人背脊发凉的故事，会将玩家的恐惧推向最高点。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >日式恐怖的巅峰</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能以第一人称视角和第三人称视角，自由地探索被诅咒的废弃医院，为鼓起勇气仔细观察的玩家提供了全新的视角。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扣人心弦的灵异现象推理作品</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有六个章节，八段额外剧情以及多个残酷的“悲惨结局”。能否抵达“真结局”，揭开藏在“彩芽的咒术仪式”背后的可怕真相，完全取决于你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
